                                    <reference internal="True" refuri="../../../classes/class_projectsettings#class-projectsettings-property-rendering-limits-time-time-rollover-secs"><inline classes="std std-ref">rollover</inline></reference>
                                    setting). It's affected by <reference internal="True" refuri="../../../classes/class_engine#class-engine-property-time-scale"><inline classes="std std-ref">time_scale</inline></reference> but not by pausing. If you need a
